‎Be aware of your position

255
00:14:39,503 --> 00:14:41,672
How about showing off your talent to the fullest?

256
00:14:41,755 --> 00:14:43,799
‎Remember‎This is how politicians get angry.

257
00:14:43,883 --> 00:14:46,135
-(Akari) Yes‎-(Mari) You don't have to remember it.

258
00:14:46,218 --> 00:14:48,470
‎I'll do my best even if you don't tell me

259
00:14:48,554 --> 00:14:50,431
‎I have prepared two secret strategies.

260
00:14:50,514 --> 00:14:51,682
(Mari) Secret plan?

261
00:14:51,765 --> 00:14:53,434
‎First of all, Part 1

262
00:14:54,226 --> 00:14:57,855
‎These 2.02 million votes

263
00:14:57,938 --> 00:14:58,772
‎Divide

264
00:14:58,856 --> 00:14:59,857
(2 people) Do you want to divide it?

265
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:02,526
Promote another candidate within the Democratic Party and compete with each other

266
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:04,278
But the recommendation from the party...

267
00:15:04,361 --> 00:15:07,323
‎Usually 1 person‎Because the votes will be split.

268
00:15:07,406 --> 00:15:08,949
‎Yes...

269
00:15:09,033 --> 00:15:11,994
‎That's why I endorse him without an endorsement and bring about a divisive election.

270
00:15:12,077 --> 00:15:14,288
‎Can you do it? That kind of thing

271
00:15:14,371 --> 00:15:18,417
‎Recommendation is in principle unanimous by the Tokyo Metropolitan Government Board of Governors.

272
00:15:19,084 --> 00:15:21,170
‎Ryusei is popular, but has many enemies.

273
00:15:21,253 --> 00:15:26,300
There must have been some people in the metropolitan area who were aware that he had made it himself and had an antipathy towards it.

274
00:15:26,383 --> 00:15:29,678
I can't come up with any other candidates.

275
00:15:29,762 --> 00:15:31,513
Under pressure from the chief secretary

276
00:15:31,597 --> 00:15:33,682
‎Cannot object publicly

277
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:35,267
‎What if that happens?

278
00:15:35,351 --> 00:15:37,061
‎Leave before making a decision

279
00:15:38,228 --> 00:15:40,356
‎Oh, so it's going to be unanimous?

280
00:15:40,439 --> 00:15:41,774
‎Naru desu

281
00:15:41,857 --> 00:15:43,108
‎1 person…

282
00:15:43,817 --> 00:15:46,862
No, there should have been two people.

283
00:15:46,946 --> 00:15:50,032
‎There is an anti-Meteor faction within the Tokyo Ren.

284
00:15:50,115 --> 00:15:51,784
First find out who it is

285
00:15:51,867 --> 00:15:52,993
‎How?

286
00:15:54,662 --> 00:15:55,496
Set up with

287
00:15:55,579 --> 00:15:56,872
‎What?

288
00:15:56,956 --> 00:15:58,957
‎It will take some time.

289
00:15:59,041 --> 00:16:02,044
In the meantime, I would like to ask the two of you for secret plan 2.

290
00:16:02,127 --> 00:16:04,296
‎Name Operation Avengers

291
00:16:05,965 --> 00:16:07,341
‎-(Igarashi) Akari-san‎-(Akari) Yes.

292
00:16:07,424 --> 00:16:09,385
‎You have charm

293
00:16:09,468 --> 00:16:11,178
‎Human power

294
00:16:11,679 --> 00:16:15,015
But when it comes to politics, I'm an amateur.

295
00:16:15,099 --> 00:16:16,850
Even after studying hard for 50 days

296
00:16:16,934 --> 00:16:19,937
‎It is impossible to build up the strength to run the metropolitan government.

297
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:21,814
Voters aren't stupid either.

298
00:16:21,897 --> 00:16:25,067
No patient entrusts their life to a doctor who works overnight.

299
00:16:25,150 --> 00:16:26,485
‎-(Mari) But... ‎-(Igarashi) Because it's ⸺

300
00:16:26,568 --> 00:16:27,736
‎Sell as a team

301
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:28,904
‎Team?

302
00:16:28,988 --> 00:16:30,114
‎Includes Deputy Governor

303
00:16:30,197 --> 00:16:33,033
(Mari) It is true that the Tokyo governor can appoint the vice governor.

304
00:16:33,117 --> 00:16:33,993
‎Parliamentary approval...

305
00:16:34,076 --> 00:16:35,786
‎It's necessary but

306
00:16:35,869 --> 00:16:38,747
At the election stage, Tokyo gubernatorial candidates select vice governor candidates.

307
00:16:38,831 --> 00:16:40,332
There's no rule that says you can't make it public.

308
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:42,084
Even in the presidential election, the vice president...

309
00:16:42,167 --> 00:16:43,419
(Mari) No, please wait.

310
00:16:43,502 --> 00:16:45,838
‎Do you mean to make it public? ‎Me and Mr. Igarashi's names

311
00:16:45,921 --> 00:16:47,548
‎Of course

312
00:16:47,631 --> 00:16:51,427
‎Hoshino Mari‎Daughter of the insulated secretary general and former secretary

313
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:54,471
No, my father... No, there was interference from the Democratic Party...

314
00:16:54,555 --> 00:16:55,556
‎Take it

315
00:16:57,433 --> 00:16:59,601
‎Obstruction is propaganda

316
00:16:59,685 --> 00:17:02,604
‎I'm 100,000,000 times more thankful than being silently killed.

317
00:17:02,688 --> 00:17:05,315
With a former snack shop mom full of humanity

318
00:17:05,399 --> 00:17:06,734
‎Challenge the Tokyo gubernatorial election

319
00:17:06,817 --> 00:17:11,071
‎Avenge of the losers who were cut off by the secretary-general of the Democratic Party

320
00:17:12,698 --> 00:17:17,745
The story we carry in order to win in this election campaign

321
00:17:22,082 --> 00:17:23,709
‎Hold your stomach, young lady

322
00:17:23,792 --> 00:17:26,295
‎You need to be prepared to commit to life.

323
00:17:27,212 --> 00:17:29,256
‎If you want to use this as a trump card

324
00:17:35,763 --> 00:17:37,973
‎-(Mari) This... ‎-(Igarashi) It reached me too.

325
00:17:39,725 --> 00:17:43,437
It is the darkness that brings the light.

326
00:17:50,027 --> 00:17:51,111
‎I understand

327
00:17:51,195 --> 00:17:52,529
‎2 more people

328
00:17:53,447 --> 00:17:56,408
The number of deputy governors that the Tokyo governor can appoint is up to four.

329
00:17:56,492 --> 00:17:58,368
While I'm dividing the votes

330
00:17:58,452 --> 00:18:00,913
‎Two of us, third Avenger‎Please woo me.

331
00:18:01,622 --> 00:18:02,790
‎Who...

332
00:18:03,415 --> 00:18:04,875
‎He's the only one there, right?

333
00:18:09,004 --> 00:18:10,255
(Hotaru) Hinata!

334
00:18:10,798 --> 00:18:12,049
‎Water bottle

335
00:18:12,132 --> 00:18:13,884
What about gym clothes? I got it

336
00:18:14,676 --> 00:18:15,969
‎Yes please

337
00:18:17,971 --> 00:18:19,556
Yes, I'm fine

338
00:18:20,682 --> 00:18:22,267
‎Courage

339
00:18:22,351 --> 00:18:24,895
‎Flower!

340
00:18:24,978 --> 00:18:26,188
‎Bloom!

341
00:18:26,271 --> 00:18:27,105
‎Yes, please come.

342
00:18:27,189 --> 00:18:28,982
-(Yota) I'm coming.-(Hotaru) Yes.

343
00:18:48,961 --> 00:18:52,881
Hey, this is a new product created by the very popular Maru-san.

344
00:18:53,674 --> 00:18:55,425
‎(Maru-san)〈Of course〉

345
00:18:58,762 --> 00:19:01,723
(Fireflies) Hey, Mom, how long will you keep it up?

346
00:19:01,807 --> 00:19:03,058
(Hotaru's mother) That's fine.

347
00:19:03,142 --> 00:19:05,519
‎Customer: It's popular, so hey?

348
00:19:05,602 --> 00:19:07,104
‎Isn't it good that it's not particularly popular?

349
00:19:07,187 --> 00:19:09,731
-(Hotaru's Mother) What about delivery? -(Hotaru) Huh?

350
00:19:09,815 --> 00:19:12,025
‎Wow, it's already been this long‎Dad, are you ready?

351
00:19:12,109 --> 00:19:13,318
(Hotaru's father) It's done.

352
00:19:13,402 --> 00:19:14,486
Because there's a typhoon tonight

353
00:19:14,570 --> 00:19:15,654
Tell me to be careful

354
00:19:15,654 --> 00:19:16,154
Tell me to be careful‎〈Tonight's typhoon〉

355
00:19:16,154 --> 00:19:16,238
‎<Typhoon tonight>

356
00:19:16,238 --> 00:19:17,239
To the elderly‎〈Tonight's typhoon〉

357
00:19:17,239 --> 00:19:17,322
‎<Typhoon tonight>

358
00:19:17,322 --> 00:19:18,365
Yes, I know‎〈Tonight's typhoon〉

359
00:19:19,616 --> 00:19:23,745
‎I'm worried about the elderly, but I'm not an old person either.

360
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:28,750
(Children's voices of joy) (Fireflies) Yes, I'll open it. Ahaha...

361
00:19:29,585 --> 00:19:32,754
‎Okay, the bread has arrived.

362
00:19:32,838 --> 00:19:36,174
-(Children) Thank you‎-(Firefly) You're welcome.

363
00:19:36,258 --> 00:19:39,595
(Firefly) These days, my favorite phrase is already...

364
00:19:39,678 --> 00:19:40,929
‎I'll blow you away

365
00:19:41,013 --> 00:19:42,055
‎I'll blow you away

366
00:19:42,139 --> 00:19:43,265
‎I'll blow you away

367
00:19:43,348 --> 00:19:44,516
‎I'll blow you away

368
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:45,893
‎I'll blow you away

369
00:19:45,976 --> 00:19:47,561
(Fireflies) Oh, good morning.

370
00:19:47,644 --> 00:19:48,896
(Fireflies) Who am I?

371
00:19:48,979 --> 00:19:51,815
What did you want to blow away so much?

372
00:19:53,525 --> 00:19:55,527
‎What could I have thrown away?

373
00:19:57,487 --> 00:20:00,657
Maybe without being able to blow anything away

374
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:05,287
‎I woke up after being blown away.

375
00:20:05,871 --> 00:20:11,335
Please, from now on, live a life that suits you.

376
00:20:12,211 --> 00:20:14,880
(Hotaru) The world was too strong for me

377
00:20:14,963 --> 00:20:16,673
‎-(Fireflies) Yes, please enjoy‎-(Customers) Thank you.

378
00:20:16,757 --> 00:20:19,009
-(Hotaru) Thank you very much‎-(Customer) I'll come again.

379
00:20:19,843 --> 00:20:21,053
‎Welcome

380
00:20:25,015 --> 00:20:26,183
‎Girl...

381
00:20:27,184 --> 00:20:28,685
It's been a long time

382
00:20:29,603 --> 00:20:31,688
Kumoi Hotaru-san

383
00:20:46,370 --> 00:20:48,747
‎It's a wonderful shop.

384
00:20:53,877 --> 00:20:54,795
‎What happened?

385
00:20:56,546 --> 00:20:57,839
‎Sorry

386
00:20:58,548 --> 00:21:00,717
The emotion of those days has come back to me

387
00:21:01,802 --> 00:21:05,764
Around this time, it was decided that the factory would be relocated.

388
00:21:05,847 --> 00:21:08,558
‎Regular customers‎Most of them were from there.

389
00:21:13,855 --> 00:21:18,110
I feel extremely anxious every day.

390
00:21:18,777 --> 00:21:19,778
(Fireflies) Sorry for keeping you waiting.

391
00:21:19,861 --> 00:21:22,614
(Mari) Ah, no, I'm sorry, all of a sudden.

392
00:21:25,909 --> 00:21:27,369
‎Don't worry about it

393
00:21:28,912 --> 00:21:31,415
Akari-san, please calm down.

394
00:21:31,498 --> 00:21:33,291
-(Hotaru) Sorry for the mess. -(Mari) Sorry to bother you.

395
00:21:33,375 --> 00:21:34,418
(Akari) Excuse me.

396
00:21:35,252 --> 00:21:36,712
(Firefly) Please sit down.

397
00:21:36,795 --> 00:21:39,006
‎-(Mari) Don't worry about that‎-(Akari) Don't worry about it

398
00:21:43,802 --> 00:21:46,930
‎Ah, on-site sales...

399
00:21:47,806 --> 00:21:49,349
(Fireflies) Shichijojima

400
00:21:49,433 --> 00:21:52,686
‎There is no bakery ‎There are not many types of bread you can buy.

401
00:21:52,769 --> 00:21:54,604
Well, there's no allergy-friendly bread either.

402
00:21:54,688 --> 00:21:56,815
‎Differences in selection by region

403
00:21:56,898 --> 00:21:59,234
That is also an issue for Tokyo.

404
00:21:59,317 --> 00:22:01,528
Ah, Shichijojima is Tokyo.

405
00:22:01,611 --> 00:22:04,948
(Hotaru) The ferry fee is expensive, so I only do it once every two months.

406
00:22:05,032 --> 00:22:07,075
‎This is a wonderful initiative.

407
00:22:07,159 --> 00:22:11,038
‎Soup kitchens to support disaster-stricken areas and people in need ‎Food distribution, etc.

408
00:22:11,121 --> 00:22:13,248
You provided bread, right?

409
00:22:13,332 --> 00:22:15,959
I heard about it from Mr. Igarashi.

410
00:22:16,543 --> 00:22:17,711
(Hotaru) Gala-san...

411
00:22:17,794 --> 00:22:20,338
‎Also active in hiring people with disabilities.

412
00:22:21,423 --> 00:22:23,383
All of our staff are regular employees.

413
00:22:24,551 --> 00:22:26,595
‎This is a wonderful initiative.

414
00:22:26,678 --> 00:22:28,180
(Hotaru) It's not like that.

415
00:22:28,263 --> 00:22:30,307
‎What they want to do What they can do

416
00:22:30,390 --> 00:22:32,684
‎What we want you to do ‎What you can do for us

417
00:22:32,768 --> 00:22:35,604
‎Because we matched, ‎I'm just working for you.

418
00:22:35,687 --> 00:22:39,649
Well, I don't think it's a problem because it's a general employment.

419
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:44,488
‎Employment of people with disabilities There may be cases where employment is the best fit for both parties.

420
00:22:44,571 --> 00:22:48,492
Type A and type B workplaces each have their own significance.

421
00:22:49,117 --> 00:22:51,703
Well, people with disabilities are lumped together.

422
00:22:51,787 --> 00:22:56,416
‎Regardless of the type of job, the legal employment rate remains the same, even if you keep increasing it.

423
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,794
In the end, that's it...

424
00:23:01,129 --> 00:23:02,464
‎Sorry, I'm fluent by myself

425
00:23:02,547 --> 00:23:04,508
No, I want to hear more.

426
00:23:04,591 --> 00:23:06,593
‎-(Light) It's a learning experience‎-(Firefly) Stop it!

427
00:23:06,676 --> 00:23:08,887
‎-(Hotaru) Sorry for being so bossy‎-(Mari/Akari) No, no...

428
00:23:10,055 --> 00:23:11,640
(Sound of door opening) (Yota) I’m home.

429
00:23:11,723 --> 00:23:13,642
(Fireflies) Hey, I'm back.

430
00:23:13,725 --> 00:23:14,935
‎Yota Welcome back

431
00:23:17,062 --> 00:23:18,897
‎Customer

432
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:21,900
‎Yota-san, I’m bothering you.‎This is Mari Hoshino.

433
00:23:21,983 --> 00:23:23,777
Hello, this is Akari Tsukioka.

434
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:25,445
(Yota: in a whisper) Hello.

435
00:23:27,155 --> 00:23:29,199
‎A modest child

436
00:23:29,282 --> 00:23:30,450
‎Please

437
00:23:31,326 --> 00:23:32,244
‎What grade are you in?

438
00:23:33,245 --> 00:23:35,747
‎1st year student? It's shiny

439
00:23:36,790 --> 00:23:39,126
(Hotaru) Yota Wash your hands and gargle

440
00:23:39,209 --> 00:23:41,670
At the store, grandma has prepared a snack for you, so go ahead and eat it.

441
00:23:44,423 --> 00:23:46,550
-(Akari) So cute‎-(Mari) Yes

442
00:23:46,633 --> 00:23:49,678
‎-(Firefly) Please‎-(Mari) Thank you.

443
00:23:51,388 --> 00:23:54,641
(Fireflies) What? Talk to me

444
00:23:57,602 --> 00:24:01,648
Kumoi-san, I have a request for you today.

445
00:24:05,443 --> 00:24:06,820
‎-(Hotaru) Impossible‎-(Akari/Mari) Huh?

446
00:24:06,903 --> 00:24:10,574
‎I thought you were talking about the lieutenant governor. Stop joking.

447
00:24:10,657 --> 00:24:13,493
-(Mari) I'm serious‎-(Hotaru) Even if it's impossible, I have a child.

448
00:24:13,577 --> 00:24:16,288
But when you were mayor, Yota was still in nursery school, right?

449
00:24:16,371 --> 00:24:18,498
It was a burden

450
00:24:18,582 --> 00:24:21,793
To Youta, to his parents, to city officials

451
00:24:22,294 --> 00:24:24,337
I always feel so guilty

452
00:24:25,714 --> 00:24:28,258
I mean, when you go to elementary school

453
00:24:28,341 --> 00:24:31,386
‎It will be easier to balance childcare and work⸺

454
00:24:31,470 --> 00:24:35,348
There is a mysterious misunderstanding, but the opposite is also true.

455
00:24:35,432 --> 00:24:37,476
Never heard of it? 1st grade wall

456
00:24:39,561 --> 00:24:40,479
‎Uneducated

457
00:24:40,562 --> 00:24:44,399
Elementary school starts later and leaves earlier than nursery school, right?

458
00:24:44,482 --> 00:24:46,776
‎You won't be able to work shorter hours

459
00:24:46,860 --> 00:24:49,237
‎There are more events, and ‎We have summer vacation.

460
00:24:49,321 --> 00:24:51,948
‎The problem of waiting lists for school children remains high.

461
00:24:52,741 --> 00:24:54,993
I'm lucky to live at home with my parents.

462
00:24:55,076 --> 00:24:57,829
My parents are fine too, so I'm doing okay.

463
00:24:57,913 --> 00:24:59,372
It's a tightrope walk

464
00:24:59,915 --> 00:25:01,500
It ends when someone falls down

465
00:25:01,583 --> 00:25:03,710
‎It's a truly important city...

466
00:25:03,793 --> 00:25:06,713
No, this is a national issue, so please join us.

467
00:25:07,506 --> 00:25:10,884
‎Without any physical or mental burden on anyone‎Without making any sacrifices

468
00:25:10,967 --> 00:25:14,638
How to balance childcare and work with career...

469
00:25:14,721 --> 00:25:15,805
(Fireflies) To find

470
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:19,559
Do you want me to make a sacrifice?

471
00:25:25,315 --> 00:25:27,400
‎Sorry, I said it in a mean way.

472
00:25:29,778 --> 00:25:32,239
But I've already given up

473
00:25:32,989 --> 00:25:36,117
I sacrifice myself and my family for others.

474
00:25:40,538 --> 00:25:42,332
‎Gara-san is free too.

475
00:25:43,583 --> 00:25:47,420
Even though Hotaru said I would protect her, she quickly ran away by herself.

476
00:25:47,504 --> 00:25:49,172
‎That's different

477
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:54,678
I didn't run away, I turned myself in.

478
00:25:54,761 --> 00:25:56,054
‎To protect

479
00:25:58,139 --> 00:26:01,726
Mr. Igarashi was seriously in love with Mr. Kumoi.

480
00:26:02,978 --> 00:26:06,356
I'm running around trying to make you a candidate recommended by the Democratic Party.

481
00:26:06,439 --> 00:26:09,401
Please lend your strength to Kumoi Hotaru

482
00:26:10,443 --> 00:26:11,486
‎I know

483
00:26:11,569 --> 00:26:14,698
It was my father who turned it over just before the notification date.

484
00:26:15,448 --> 00:26:17,033
‎Become chairman of the supporter's association

485
00:26:17,117 --> 00:26:19,536
A father was asked to make his son mayor.

486
00:26:20,453 --> 00:26:23,456
‎Recommendations taken from you

487
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:25,959
‎Election support has also been discontinued.

488
00:26:28,878 --> 00:26:31,047
I ordered the chairman's son to win.

489
00:26:31,131 --> 00:26:33,174
‎I know that too

490
00:26:34,759 --> 00:26:36,469
But Mr. Gala

491
00:26:36,553 --> 00:26:39,139
Thank you for continuing to support me secretly behind the scenes.

492
00:26:39,222 --> 00:26:40,515
‎I became the mayor

493
00:26:40,598 --> 00:26:44,561
When his father found out, Mr. Igarashi was fired.

494
00:26:46,479 --> 00:26:48,732
‎If I get involved any more

495
00:26:48,815 --> 00:26:52,235
Mr. Kumoi may be removed from his position as mayor.

496
00:26:52,319 --> 00:26:53,236
So Mr. Igarashi...

497
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:56,448
Although I was dragged down, in the end

498
00:26:58,241 --> 00:27:02,245
‎I'm really sorry.

499
00:27:04,581 --> 00:27:06,833
‎Sorry‎I said something mean again.

500
00:27:07,709 --> 00:27:10,211
There's nothing for a young lady to apologize for.

501
00:27:10,295 --> 00:27:11,630
‎I chose it.

502
00:27:11,713 --> 00:27:12,547
