00:43:52,630 --> 00:43:53,756
yeah?

758
00:43:53,839 --> 00:43:55,049
picture?

759
00:44:00,596 --> 00:44:02,473
Wow, that's amazing.

760
00:44:03,098 --> 00:44:04,433
(Subaru) Mari Hoshino

761
00:44:04,516 --> 00:44:07,436
It seems that he has started running a public bathhouse.

762
00:44:08,896 --> 00:44:12,232
Sorry, Subaru, please explain slowly.

763
00:44:12,316 --> 00:44:14,360
oh sorry

764
00:44:17,905 --> 00:44:20,866
Mari Hoshino is

765
00:44:20,949 --> 00:44:22,284
To manage a public bath...

766
00:44:22,368 --> 00:44:24,870
(Ryusei) Oh, I'm sorry, that's not true.

767
00:44:33,629 --> 00:44:34,922
picture?

768
00:44:47,684 --> 00:44:49,103
(Mari) Akari Tsukioka

769
00:44:49,186 --> 00:44:50,521
Let's work together to make things brighter

770
00:44:50,604 --> 00:44:51,522
(Toru) Prepare it.

771
00:44:51,605 --> 00:44:52,940
-(Mari) So... -(Akari) Did you do it?

772
00:44:53,023 --> 00:44:55,192
(Takaomi) I could see it all the time, inside your belly.

773
00:44:55,275 --> 00:44:57,152
(Ryusei) Can I leave you a message?

774
00:44:57,820 --> 00:44:59,446
(Mari) Please do it for me!

775
00:44:59,530 --> 00:45:00,364
Huh!

776
00:45:01,532 --> 00:45:03,325
(Amemiya) Mari-san, isn't she my god?

777
00:45:03,409 --> 00:45:05,202
(Mari) Being dependent on someone is a nuisance.

778
00:45:05,285 --> 00:45:07,121
(Igarashi) Me and Hotaru will split the votes.

779
00:45:07,204 --> 00:45:10,582
(Mari) If things continue like this, the secretary-general's dog will win.

780
00:45:10,666 --> 00:45:12,960
(Everyone) We'll win! Let's win!

781
00:45:13,043 --> 00:45:14,795
-(Mari) We'll win! -(Akari and others) We'll win!

782
00:45:14,878 --> 00:45:16,004
(Mari) I'll win!

783
00:45:16,088 --> 00:45:17,631
(Akari and others) We'll win!
